{
  "texts": [
    "The Self-Instruct construction framework used in the dataset has been widely applied.",
    "• ShareChat 87.",
    "The ShareChat dataset comprises approximately 90K instructions, all sourced from dialogue data on ShareGPT.",
    "In terms of language distribution, there are 68K instructions in English, 11K in Chinese, and the remaining in other languages.",
    "The aim of this dataset is to translate all instructions in other languages into Chinese, contributing to the resources of Chinese instructions."
  ]
}